mbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33XM17D.jpg&h=7fa7a446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIOS已出<br />\n啱啱收到email"},{"pid":"76bf85d85e67b2208c3cc3da1f956a12e2e2303e","tid":122300,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33XM17D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33XM17D.jpg&h=7fa7a446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIOS已出<br />\n啱啱收到email</blockquote><br />\n屌 膠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661a7fd9dda81918301f2ffd5b4af93c427941fa","tid":122300,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"試玩左一陣<br />\n個手感好難習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日避同攻擊個制都調亂左<br />\n我用開長劍,個攻擊速度好似慢左小小<br />\n同埋大炮儲op個動作快左<br />\n唔知係咪太耐無玩既錯覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n視角我玩開慣左唔LOCK怪<br />\n但係用手機唔LOCK怪手動轉視角既慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫面感覺上人物模組細緻左<br />\n但其它方面仲衰過PSP年代果隻<br />\n但係邊方面我又唔識講<br />\n唯一可以講既係捕食果陣畫面果個特效柒到唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接一野張圖半透明放上畫面算鳩數咁<br />\n<br />\n不過忠實死忠為左等官方出alisa吸金<br />\n我點一定會繼續玩落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4838d8bc84027bcb05f0d5265fbbdd1ce5755b","tid":122300,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"Game都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時覺得轉視點比較辛苦<br />\n其他尚可接受"},{"pid":"8a02f1f648633e98a6d35329e7878215e7d96980","tid":122300,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"玩左一陣覺得都有d似monster hunter,都係有類似集會所既野"},{"pid":"a98341ef454f41fe26df775670e45f6f8a7c7451","tid":122300,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔知咩事 我係咁連唔到入隻GAME 屋企WIFI問題定係太大負荷"},{"pid":"0ece0ee0c96cdb3c778db8bc69b484f9b10c222e","tid":122300,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"I 都出左  屎忽痕碌app store 見到 竟然默默地出左"},{"pid":"2da02521d89ee925dadfc1f295e6ccbfd73aca58","tid":122300,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知咩事 我係咁連唔到入隻GAME 屋企WIFI問題定係太大負荷</blockquote><br />\nServer問題 日本都係咁"},{"pid":"b1e18d747840c6ba79b58f8df41347eb16015b7f","tid":122300,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"佢課金係課邊方面"},{"pid":"74f3e44108651f03a16a07860f6ef9d6bd0aa05b","tid":122300,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢課金係課邊方面</blockquote><br />\n我都唔清楚 入GAME完左教學關冇耐就彈左出去"},{"pid":"b1f7c9ecc7e8fa2ca4182f08f453f2eac0dfa086","tid":122300,"uid":52494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"更到2046都未入到game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db44d6745babdb3382641fb7f82548240d15f089","tid":122300,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:09:11.000Z","msg":"預左玩唔到,仲多人連線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2deac4fabcdf9e47ac5d6cda46a2d467ca20f1d8","tid":122300,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢課金係課邊方面</blockquote><br />\n我都唔清楚 入GAME完左教學關冇耐就彈左出去</blockquote><br />\n應該主要抽野<br />\n其次開倉開所持<br />\n抽野分武器同服裝兩邊<br />\n冇得揀細項抽(eg. 只抽近戰)<br />\n三抽中一把四星槍二三星盾<br />\n只睇數值三星都有初期裝幾倍<br />\n但佢有得自己造武<br />\n暫時未知抽係唔係必須品定只係方便你快刷<br />\n服裝方面抽嘅應該會有少少特殊能力<br />\n(換衫度有一格特性 但估計影響唔大)<br />\n<br />\n搞得手機game實屈你課金<br />\n希望唔會變課長先玩到<br />\n真心如果佢唔係話係正傳故事一部分我都未必會玩"},{"pid":"e7095cf76f3628d9cbf347a285312deee9c0da81","tid":122300,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"講漏左少少<br />\n抽野衫平啲 單抽三石 十抽廿七<br />\n武器 單抽五石 十抽四十五<br />\n抽完之後要喺抽野嗰頁個box度收<br />\n再返基地倉庫拎 都幾麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659b1a0128ec892dcd0b7fd32eaf3035a5338266","tid":122300,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩左一陣覺得都有d似monster hunter,都係有類似集會所既野</blockquote><br />\n第一代係psp食住mh條水既眾多產物之一黎<br />\n之後靠得住先慢慢發展成一個系列<br />\n隻game我覺得比較有特色係個神機（把武器）<br />\n近戰遠攻同堆盾都集中哂係一部野度<br />\n同埋子陣編輯系統<br />\n不過今代個系統好似斬左無得自己編輯<br />\n個垃圾捕食系統宣傳果陣話就話係特色<br />\n不過去到最新一代先實用<br />\n但係今代個捕食系統好似又返翻第1.5代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f803f390e1ab6247681da55d7ef19197cf4783a","tid":122300,"uid":19550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:03:23.000Z","msg":"連patch都down唔曬<br />\ndown到最後四個就不停話連線問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589a55f047bc65eb248ef3a08d8e0a5334147d11","tid":122300,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"睇黎應該唔過返幾個星期都玩唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6d97d9a9894d623bc84949b8ec2a4ccd991c6a","tid":122300,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"on9 e個年代仲會因人流問題爆ser<br />\n佢game入面個server仲要係分12345678果種<br />\n到底係咪00年代既產物黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係返去玩住隻濕鳩龍project好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63bdd9ddba4b673ac8abc2e155da8862365acda","tid":122300,"uid"